<%# /teams -- Track 3 destination. Coordinate Your Team (L7-L8). v7 layout. %>
<style>
  .tm-step { transition:transform .22s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), box-shadow .22s ease, border-color .22s ease; }
  .tm-step:hover { transform:translateY(-4px); border-color:rgba(13,125,242,.35);
    box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(20,22,28,.06), 0 26px 50px -24px rgba(20,22,28,.26); }
  .tm-num {
    width:42px; height:42px; border-radius:12px; flex:none;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Schibsted Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:800; font-size:17px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(13,125,242,.12),rgba(13,125,242,.05));
    color:var(--blue-deep); border:1px solid rgba(13,125,242,.25);
  }
  .tm-orgy { animation:tm-orgy 7s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes tm-orgy { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(0);} 50%{transform:translateY(-12px) rotate(-3deg);} }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){ .tm-orgy{ animation:none; } }
</style>

<!-- ================= HERO ================= -->
<section class="bg-[var(--white)]">
  <div class="max-w-[1080px] mx-auto px-6 pt-[124px] pb-16 sm:pt-[148px] sm:pb-20">
    <nav class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--ink-mute)] flex items-center gap-2 mb-7">
      <a href="/" class="link-u" style="border-bottom-width:1.5px;">OTP</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-[var(--ink-soft)]">Coordinate your team</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-14">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-4 flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <span class="tick" style="background:var(--blue);"></span>
          Track 3 &middot; Your team is running agents &middot; L7&ndash;L8
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-[var(--ink)]"
            style="font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4.6vw,3.6rem); line-height:1.07; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.025em;">
          Multiple humans. Multiple agents. <span class="text-[var(--blue)]">One operating layer.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.6] max-w-[36rem] mt-5">
          You are past the solo stage. Several people are now running agents on different parts of the business. They are operating in silos, duplicating work, and nobody can see the full stack at once.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.7] max-w-[36rem] mt-4">
          This track is about turning a fleet of disconnected agents into a coordinated team. Four steps: multi-user permissions, a cross-team agent registry, an inter-agent message bus so agents can talk to each other directly, and Bassim's L8 maturity score across the org so you can see where you actually are.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative shrink-0" style="width:200px; max-width:48vw;">
        <img src="/public/orgy-cut.png" alt="Orgy, the OTP mascot"
             class="tm-orgy relative block w-full" style="filter:drop-shadow(0 20px 30px rgba(20,22,28,.2));">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= FOUR STEPS ================= -->
<section class="bg-[var(--grey)]">
  <div class="max-w-[920px] mx-auto px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="eyebrow mb-3" style="color:var(--blue-deep);">The four steps</div>
    <h2 class="font-display text-[var(--ink)] tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.1] mb-10"
        style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3.2vw,2.4rem); font-weight:700;">
      From a fleet of silos to a coordinated team.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-5">

      <a href="/dashboard/team" class="tm-step card block p-7 sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="tm-num">1</div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-display text-[var(--ink)] text-[1.3rem] sm:text-[1.45rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.01em]">Set up multi-user with role permissions</h3>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--ink-mute)]">~ 30 min</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[14.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.7] mb-4">Invite your team. Decide who can edit which agents, see which KPIs, approve which SOPs. Most agent failures at this stage are not technical, they are permission ambiguity. Two people editing the same agent's SOP at the same time. Get the boundaries clear early.</p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--blue-deep)]">Open team setup &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/graph" class="tm-step card block p-7 sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="tm-num">2</div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-display text-[var(--ink)] text-[1.3rem] sm:text-[1.45rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.01em]">Build the cross-agent registry</h3>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--ink-mute)]">~ 45 min</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[14.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.7] mb-4">Every agent across every team in one chart. Sales agents, ops agents, support agents, finance agents, visible to everyone with permission. This is the moment people stop saying "we have AI in finance" and start saying "we have 23 agents on the chart." It changes the conversation.</p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--blue-deep)]">Open the org chart &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/protocol" class="tm-step card block p-7 sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="tm-num">3</div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-display text-[var(--ink)] text-[1.3rem] sm:text-[1.45rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.01em]">Wire up the inter-agent message bus</h3>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--ink-mute)]">~ 1 hr</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[14.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.7] mb-4">Agents talking to other agents directly, not through a human in the middle. The sales agent flags a churn risk to the retention agent. The pacing agent notifies the analytics agent of a budget anomaly. This is L8 territory: agent-to-agent coordination without a human bottleneck.</p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--blue-deep)]">Configure the bus &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/dashboard" class="tm-step card block p-7 sm:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="tm-num">4</div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-display text-[var(--ink)] text-[1.3rem] sm:text-[1.45rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.01em]">Turn on Bassim L8 maturity scoring</h3>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--ink-mute)]">Continuous</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[14.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.7] mb-4">Get a live score on where your org is on Bassim Eledath's 8 Levels of Agentic Engineering. Not a vanity number, a diagnostic. Where are you stuck? Which level is the bottleneck? Which agents are pulling you up? Which are pulling you down? This is the dashboard your leadership team meets around.</p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-[var(--blue-deep)]">Open your maturity score &rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= WHAT'S NEXT ================= -->
<section class="bg-[var(--white)]">
  <div class="max-w-[920px] mx-auto px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="card p-8 sm:p-11">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-3" style="color:var(--green-deep);">When you are past this</div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-[var(--ink)] tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.12] mb-3"
          style="font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.3rem); font-weight:700;">
        Become a Certified OTP Integrator.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.72] max-w-[40rem] mb-7">
        You are running an agent-mature org. You probably know other companies that are not there yet and need help getting there. The OTP Partner Program lets you implement OTP for clients, run their orgs from your dashboard, and earn revenue share, with a Certified OTP Integrator badge that signals you have actually done it.
      </p>
      <a href="/partners" class="btn-ink inline-block px-7 py-3.5 text-[15px]">Become a partner &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
